Package uk.co.crider.jablus.gui

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    UserInterface
    Provides methods which the simulation uses to access the interactive user interface.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DisplayParams
    Used to control general display parameters.
    EventHandler
    Instances of this class handle all user generated events
    Field
    Simple class to represent a field with a label and value
    FileChooser
    Used for selecting files to open/save
    GridView
    Represents a grid of values
    JablusWindow
    Basic top level jablus window, with jablus logo and status bar.
    Popup
    Generates and displays popups
    Table
    Extention of JTable object representing a scrollable table
    ToolBar
    For holding rows of tool buttons
    ToolButton
    Convenience subclass of JButton for creating tool buttons
